{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fccabf97b4","title":"毛泽东对八三四一部队支工工作的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"77524be749","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"fccabf97b4"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0cdea24855","type":"title","text":"对八三四一部队支工工作的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fccabf97b4"},{"id":"12fdd54ab8","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fccabf97b4"},{"id":"a3cd91fd4c","type":"paragraph","text":"1．下去后要做好宣传工作，要做深入的、细致的、艰苦的思想政治工作。厂子里女工多，要派些女同志下去，便于工作。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fccabf97b4"},{"id":"4155272dac","type":"paragraph","text":"2．下去后不要匆匆忙忙急于表态，经过调查研究，如果两派都是革命的群众组织，就要逐步地把他们联合起来。就是两派严重对立的群众组织，群众也是愿意联合的，不愿意联合的只是少数的几个头头。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fccabf97b4"},{"id":"bcd25d2a92","type":"paragraph","text":"3．要向工人群众学习，不怕犯错误，错了就改。要关心群众的生活，组织个医疗组，给他们看病。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fccabf97b4"}],"page":{"id":"ca13412a54","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"fccabf97b4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}